ilosophical or theoretical views and explains how they all count as post-Marxist.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Mrz 2024) 0aCommunism. 0aMarxian economics. 0aPhilosophy, Marxist. 4aCultural Studies : Cultural Studies. 4aLiterature : Literary Theory. 4aPolitics and Law : Marxism. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / History & Theory.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013z978311148737340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791484029423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791484029/original  a978-3-11-148737-3  SUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles